title: Qonuni Jumḣurii Tojikiston
titles: Qonuni Jumḣurii Tojikiston Dar borai maorif.

Qonuni Jumḣurii Tojikiston Dar borai tamghaḣoi molī va tamghaḣoi khizmatrasonī = Zakon Respubliki Tadzhikistan O tovarnykh znakakh i znakakh obsluzhivanii︠a︡ = Law of the Republic of Tajikistan On Trademarks and Service Marks.
Qonuni Jumḣurii Tojikiston Dar borai maqomoti prokuraturai Jumḣurii Tojikiston.
Qonuni Jumḣurii Tojikiston dar borai faʺolii︠a︡ti operativī-justujūī = Zakon Respubliki Tadzhikistan Ob operativno-rozysknoĭ dei︠a︡telʹnosti.
Qonuni Jumḣurii Tojikiston Dar borai muboriza bar ziddi korrupsii︠a︡ = Zakon Respubliki Tadzhikistan O borʹbe s korrupt︠s︡ieĭ.

Qonuni Jumḣurii Tojikiston Dar borai Vakolatdor oid ba ḣuquqi inson dar Jumḣurii Tojikiston = Zakon Respubliki Tadzhikistan Ob Upolnomochennom po pravam cheloveka v Respublike Tadzhikistan = Law of the Republic of Tajikistan On the Human Rights Commissioner for Human Rights in the Republic of Tajikistan.

Qonuni Jumḣurii Tojikiston Dar borai matbuot va digar vositaḣoi akhbori omma = Zakon Respubliki Tadzhikistan O pechati i drugikh sredstvakh massovoĭ informat︠s︡ii ; Qonuni Jumḣurii Tojikiston Dar borai tabʺu nashr = Zakon Respubliki Tadzhikistan Ob izdatelʹskom dele ; Qoidaḣoi baḣisobgirii tashkilotḣoi tabʺu nashr va faʺolii︠a︡ti tabʺu nashri shakhsoni ḣuquqī = Pravila uchëta izdatelʹskikh organizat︠s︡iĭ i izdatelʹskoĭ dei︠a︡telʹnosti i︠u︡ridicheskikh lit︠s︡ ; Qoidaḣoi firistodani nuskhaḣoi roĭgoni nazoratī va ḣatmii matbuoti davrī ba maqomot va tashkilotḣoi dakhldori davlatī = Pravila rassylki besplatnykh kontrolʹnykh i obi︠a︡zatelʹnykh ėkzempli︠a︡rov periodicheskoĭ pechati v sootvetstvui︠u︡shchie gosudarstvennye organy, uchrezhdenii︠a︡ i organizat︠s︡ii.
Qonuni Jumḣurii Tojikiston "Dar borai maorif" = Zakon Respubliki Tadzhikistan "Ob obrazovanii".
Qonuni Jumḣurii Tojikiston "Dar borai ishoraḣoi jughrofī" = Zakon Respubliki Tadzhikistan "O geograficheskikh ukazanii︠a︡kh" = Law of the Republic of Tajikistan "On Geographical Indications."

Qonuni Jumḣurii Tojikiston Dar borai ḣifzi ḣuquqii topologii︠a︡ḣoi mikroskhemaḣoi integralī = Zakon Respubliki Tadzhikistan O pravovoĭ okhrane topologiĭ intergalʹnykh mikroskhem = Law of the Republic of Tajikistan On the Legal Protection of the Topologies on Integrated Circuits.
Qonuni Jumḣurii Tojikiston Dar borai ikhtiroʺ = Zakon Respubliki Tadzhikistan Ob izobretenii︠a︡kh = Law of the Republic of Tajikistan On Inventions.
Qonuni Jumḣurii Tojikiston "Dar borai ozodii vijdon va ittiḣodii︠a︡ḣoi dinī" = Zakon Respubliki Tadzhikistan "O svobode sovesti i religioznykh obʺedinenii︠a︡kh"
Qonuni Jumḣurii Tojikiston "Dar borai faʺolii︠a︡ti operativī-justujūī."
Qonuni Jumḣurii Tojikiston "Dar borai sanadḣoi meʺërii ḣuquqī" = Zakon Respubliki Tadzhikistan "O normativnykh pravovykh aktakh".
Qonuni Jumḣurii Tojikiston Dar borai khizmati davlatī = Zakon Respubliki Tadzhikistan O gosudarstvennoĭ sluzhbe.
Qonuni Jumḣurii Tojikiston "Dar borai namunaḣoi sanoatī" = Zakon Respubliki Tadzhikistan "O promyshlennykh obrazt︠s︡akh" = Law of the Republic of Tajikistan "On Industrial Designs."

Quy định mới về xử phạt vi phạm hành chính trong lĩnh vực giao thông đường thủy nội địa, thống kê, đo đạc và bản đồ, tài nguyên nước, công trình thủy lợi.
